stomers comprises an outstanding list of bluechip companies including airbus boeing general electric lockheed martin raytheon snecma group united technologies and various aftermarket channels  longtime industrial customers applied materials caterpillar hitachi construction machinery komatsu america parkerhannifin corporation and various aftermarket distributors including applied industrial technologies kaman corporation and motion industries among many others rbc employees bring a wealth of experience in bearing technology to our global organization and it is this experience that has brought us to the leadership position that we hold in our industry today  this is an exciting time in our corporate history – a time of growth and a time of incredible opportunity – and we seek talented new people who are excited about meeting the challenges of nextgeneration applications in our target markets around the world positions available please email your resume to the recruiter whose email address appears in the ad with the job title in the subject line if you are an individual with disabilities who needs accommodation or you are having difficulty using our website to apply for employment please contact deepa thapa at  extension  httpswwweeocgovemployerspostercfm please select from the following criteria to view available career opportunities at rbc job category select a category all engineering administrative product management accounting salesmarketing human resources it customer service manufacturing manufacturing management productionoperations materials quality job location select a location all baldwin park ca ball ground ga bishopville sc bremen in engineered components fairfield ct fountain valley ca franklin in garden grove ca hartsville sc mentor oh middlebury ct oklahoma city ok oxford ct plymouth in rancho dominguez ca reynosa tams mexico cp san diego ca santa ana ca santa fe springs ca tecate baja california mexico torrington ct west trenton nj westminster sc     